{"tid":2507624,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度召退役軍醫支援 英中物資運抵","createTime":"2021-04-28T06:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T06:43:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6565ffd9f983e4f807dc375e9e5fc8e309ebc22","tid":2507624,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:30:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210428/OKYU3WODK5AMTLCRA3XY6DTDTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210428%2FOKYU3WODK5AMTLCRA3XY6DTDTU%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0vYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=8619580d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210428%2FOKYU3WODK5AMTLCRA3XY6DTDTU%2F&h=a9c0d2a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210428/OKYU3WODK5AMTLCRA3XY6DTDTU/</a><br />\n<br />\n印度召退役軍醫支援 英中物資運抵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mGQ5OxrPNyW7MOkDqq5GiFKWsMc=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E5XCAG5AQFACFGZTWT6GLSOKLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmGQ5OxrPNyW7MOkDqq5GiFKWsMc%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE5XCAG5AQFACFGZTWT6GLSOKLE.jpg&h=32369b47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■印度大批死者被集體火葬。路透社<br />\n<br />\n印度連續六日新增逾30萬宗確診，當局調派軍人及退休醫療兵作支援；英國、中國首批援助物資已抵達當地。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美倉底疫苗援外國 6,000萬劑AZ救急  公平組織：豁免專利更實際<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再增32萬確診<br />\n<br />\n當地昨日新增32萬宗確診個案，比前日的35萬稍為回落，但專家警告很大程度是因檢測數量大幅下降，而非感染人數減少。新德里等多地醫院床位續爆滿，氧氣嚴重短缺。軍人急忙運送軍方的後備氧氣、氧氣樽等到醫院。<br />\n<br />\n面對醫療人員工作量大增的問題，當局調派軍方總部工作的醫護至各地醫院作支援；在過去兩年退休的醫療兵，都被緊急召回至鄰近醫院工作。政府又呼籲已退休的醫護返回前線協助。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：拜登督促逆轉困局 美變疫苗領袖<br />\n<br />\n英國首批援助物資抵達當地，印度外交部發言人巴奇在社交平台Twitter上載照片，顯示一架飛機正在卸下物資，並寫道：「這是國際合作的運作。」首批物資包括100部呼吸機及95部氧氣機；另外亦有495部氧氣機、120部非侵入性正壓呼吸機、20部手動呼吸機於本周稍後送抵。<br />\n<br />\n多國繼續運送物資，中國捐贈的800部呼吸機亦已抵達當地。美國白宮疫情統籌專員齊恩茲則表示，拜登政府正致力協助提供當地主要所需物資，包括個人防護設備（PPE）、檢測設備等。世界衞生組織總幹事譚德塞則指，印度的情況令人心碎，將作出一切努力，向其提供重要設備及物資。另外，澳洲暫時禁止由印度的直航航班飛抵當地，措施至少維持至下月15日。<br />\n<br />\n德新社/路透社/美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OxfXUYeEOrVqTJj-B9ayMyYKBo4=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RCNS6P4YBVD35OIA3MLIKPGUBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOxfXUYeEOrVqTJj-B9ayMyYKBo4%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRCNS6P4YBVD35OIA3MLIKPGUBE.jpg&h=053f74b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■英國首批救援物資運抵印度。路透社"},{"pid":"88749d242c6221079faacd0782679abd105a7b5b","tid":2507624,"uid":99941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:32:32.000Z","msg":"希望班咖喱可以記住邊個係殺父仇人"},{"pid":"37ea5c48a3158f32c74ce13b8459f63c6d16185e","tid":2507624,"uid":393810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"蝻亞強姦犯大國抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535294bbaf43e6997e24989fddfba0cf3c410169","tid":2507624,"uid":377617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37ea5c48a3158f32c74ce13b8459f63c6d16185e","tid":2507624,"uid":393810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"蝻亞強姦犯大國抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" 